summary: A new texture for the wench dress and boots.
descriptionHtml:
::: Re-textured wench dress :::

(don\'t forget to endorse if you like it :)

Textures: Wolbryne
Model: original

Mod info: A new texture for the wench dress and boots. It looked kind of boring before. This will spice it all up :)

Requirements: Skyrim

Conflicts: It modifies the vanilla wench dress and boots. so it will overwrite anything else that changes the wench- dress and boots.

Location: Bar wenches throughout skyrim. or simply use the console code for it (000D191F for the dress and 000D1921 for the boots) .

Permissions: You\'re allowed to use this texture in whatever mod you want just credit me for it.

Credits and thanks: thanks to skyrim for not crashing too many times while looking at the dress in game during the creation phase.


Enjoy!

/Wolbryne
author: Wolbryne
